{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_09_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 頑張るあなたを応援するわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666669051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう。今日もこれから恋愛相談か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. Giving love advice again today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0333335717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7000007152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、サプライズ企画の収録で\nまたファンの相談に乗ってきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I'll be giving advice to fans again\nfor the recording of the surprise project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4666673819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "表情が暗いな……\nまだ悩んでいるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem down…\nAre you still worried?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1820226032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.4000003974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "悩むに決まってるじゃないですか\n私に恋愛相談なんて向いてないんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I'm worried.\nI'm not suited for giving love advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2711389561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.4000003974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私なんかに相談するんでしょう\nもっとふさわしい人が他にいると思うのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would they ask someone like me…\nI'm sure there are more suitable people out there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6000003974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……一つ質問していいか？\n怜なら恋愛相談するとしたら誰にする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Can I ask you a question?\nWho would you consult with if you needed love advice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7520000298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0333352566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私は恋愛なんてしてませんけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never been in love though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333352566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "例えばの話だ。恋愛じゃなくてもいい。悩んだり\n迷ったりした時に相談したい相手を思い浮かべてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just an example. It doesn't even have to be about love. Imagine\nsomeone you'd want to talk to when you're troubled or lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6837714036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2666648865
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "…………思い浮かべました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……I have someone in mind now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5666690985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.5333357651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜は、どうしてその人に相談しようと思ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did you think to ask that person?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5333357651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "それは……信頼出来る人だからです\n私の話を真剣に聞いて、親身になって考えてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… they’re someone I can trust.\nThey listen to me seriously and think about my problems sincerely…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7364458218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.333336528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "この人なら、迷っている私の背中を\n押してくれると思ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That person… would back me up\nwhen I’m hesitant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1666683356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666698614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "きっとファンのみんなも同じだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure your fans feel the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666698614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "怜なら、迷っている自分の背中を押してくれる\nそう思ったから相談したんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They asked you because they thought‚\n“Rei would back me up.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6000015258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4000024318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛に詳しいかどうかは関係ない……\n信頼出来て、一緒に答えを考えてくれる人だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not about knowledge of love…\nBecause that person is trustworthy and finds the answer with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4333342393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0000024318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "迷っている自分の背中を押してくれる人だから\n相談したいと思った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because that person backs me up when I hesitate…\nThat's why I want to ask them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5882372289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.800007518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌のインタビュー、ライブのMC、テレビで歌う姿\n……ファンはいつも怜を見ている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Magazine interviews‚ concert MCs‚ singing on TV…\nYour fans are always watching you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4536766261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから分かるんだ。怜がひたむきで、真っ直ぐで\n勇気をもらえるアイドルだってことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how they know. That Rei is a sincere‚ straightforward\nidol who gives them courage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.6000003973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "一ノ瀬怜なら、一歩踏み出す勇気をくれる……\nだから相談したいと思ってくれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ichinose Rei would encourage them to take a step forward…\n…That's why they wanted to ask me for advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2197549343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8666670639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛経験なんて関係ない……\n私は私らしく答えればいいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't matter if I have dating experience…\nI just have to answer in my own way‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9666655381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.6333337306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nおかげで気持ちが楽になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nThat made me feel a lot better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4666655381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "悩んでいるみんなが一歩踏み出せるように\n私なりに精一杯応援してみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that everyone who's struggling can take a step forward‚\nI’ll try my best to cheer them in my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5999988715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8666670639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "その意気だ。……ところで、ちょっと気になったんだが\nさっき怜は相談する相手に誰を想像したんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the spirit! …By the way‚ there’s something I’m curious about.\nWho did you imagine as the person you’d ask for advice earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7666787624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "それは……だ、誰でもいいじゃないですか！\n言う必要はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that's… W-whoever‚ it doesn't matter!\nI don't have to tell you!",
